task.summary: Default task
Little enhancment on the QueueCommand to make the thumbnail the video url as default, or use the bot avatar if none
Added a primary version of a Pause command, to pause the sound playing + refactored the name of some command aliases
Deleted a trailing '
Securization on the autoRole
Made the Queue Command a bit more graphic
Fixed a bug that would appear with the new way of !loop to work with !skip command
Modified log to have some stats on the bot usage :)
Reworked the help message of sound commands
!sound is now !play
Fix thread concurrency for a better experience
Added sharding to enable the bot growth
Added persistency on the !vol command
Help update on Volume command
Fixed info command, work now with sharding
Fixed setGame command to impact all servers
Fixed a bug on soundPlayerCommand
Securization on property saving :)
Fixed a bug that would appear if NPE on property
Fixed some NPE that would be logged by the bot
Added persistency on the !loop command
Deleted some useless logs
Added shuffle command and worked out the structure of the project
Set the shard ammount to 5, to gain on booting speed
Fixed a bug that would make the bot try to autorole when not supposed to.
Tech: Worked on securization about message sending, and bot permissions
Tech: Added loggin system to enhance debugging
Tech: Cleaned the project, and set the logs on commands ;)
Tech: Enhanced logs detail with better bug discovery
Tech: Modified logs roll to split 1 file per day
Tech: Removed log that showed up on when helped was needed
Tech: Added the command that caused the bug to happen in logs
Tech: Securization on Youtube call that would make the sound playing fail sometimes
Tech: Refactor properties handling for more extensibility
Feat: Added !state command that shows the server settings ;)
Feat: Better display on !queue if no track played since bot reboot
Fix: Fixed a bug that would appear on !loop if no track was played before calling the command
Fix: Fixed a bug that would appear if Youtube won't find requested track
Feat: Worked on the Property system + Added the possibility to set the bot's prefix !
Fix: Shard ammount to 5 and not 1 (woops)
Fix: Technical exception that would be thrown if an image was send
Fix: Success message would be send to owner unless the command !setGame failed xD
Fix: A bug that would appear if bot send a private message
Fix: Securization on private messages : Not between bots
Feat: Search with youtube URL :D
Fix: Issue on !ban command
Feat: Send a private message to someone who request a !ban or !kick which is successful
Chore: Reinstalled tech env + securization on logging system
Feat(Command): Added !invite
Feat(Visual): Modified display of some commands
